{"tid":1068671,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好鍾意唱k","createTime":"2019-03-19T11:34:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T05:20:57.000Z","uid":134548,"like":10,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"735d91f29f84401965f81d7951b15f2844cf5b2c","tid":1068671,"uid":134548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"本身唱歌麻麻加上有少少毒<br />\n唔敢係大班朋友面前唱<br />\n但後來識左班唔知醜既friend之後<br />\n飲左少少酒就開始黎料 瘋狂點歌唱歌，當正自己係k歌之王。<br />\n當然啦 唱到依家以k歌水準黎講已經叫好聽（d唔熟既朋友都係咁講）<br />\n<br />\n每次必點既歌係eason翻唱既一生中最愛（會扮埋校長個唱腔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）同鄭中基既閉目入神<br />\n唔知大家唱k唱開咩歌呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f06d182cee9cf1371aae5302f38b31d0b9e00269","tid":1068671,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"錄嚟聽下"},{"pid":"86c8e73c9b07ecccc88e746357aab84e4825f4de","tid":1068671,"uid":134548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f06d182cee9cf1371aae5302f38b31d0b9e00269","tid":1068671,"uid":48579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"錄嚟聽下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"片就有，下次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab4ee0c71e6ef92e7ff66d5d0ebe1ddc73b2f0b","tid":1068671,"uid":70362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"每次都唱死了都要愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c938932702095fa8be4cee8e42cb3d2b93da15","tid":1068671,"uid":134548,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ab4ee0c71e6ef92e7ff66d5d0ebe1ddc73b2f0b","tid":1068671,"uid":70362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:44:50.000Z","msg":"每次都唱死了都要愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T11:47:45.000Z","msg":"勁喎，我淨係飲多左先勉強唱到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\"